Pupil install on Fedora 25
==========================

Install Fedora 25 spin Xfce. Xfce is a more stable desktop than gnome-shell.

Disk partitions
---------------

- /dev/sda1 50 GiB XFS mounted on /
- /dev/sda2 5 GiB swap
- /dev/sda3 [rest of the disk] XFS mounted on /home

OS post-install
---------------

# dnf upgrade
reboot
